org.youscope.common.resource

Interface Resource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component, java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CellDetectionAddon, CellVisualizationAddon, DropletControllerResource, DropletObserverResource, FocusScoreResource, FocusSearchResource, SaveSettings
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResourceAdapter, StandardSaveSettings

    public interface Resource
extends Component
    A resource is some configurable object which can be used by jobs during a measurement. This interface represents the base class of other interfaces which should specify the functionality which can be carried out by this resource.
    Author:
    Moritz Lang
